Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会对我的想法和感觉做出反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like it reacts to my thoughts and my feelings and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得它感受到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think it sensed how much
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有多么想让你再次看到我原本的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted you to see me as myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有多么  渴望我们之间的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, how much I, uh, longed for that connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么可以招待你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I get you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你提起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从昨天早上起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't actually eaten anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没吃过东西了  所以我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since yesterday morning, so I--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  这可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, no, no, that won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可能有些饼干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There may be some crackers over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alec?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们这有些番石榴  李子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, looks like we got some guava, plums,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来个芒果怎么样  -李子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- mango maybe. - Uh, plum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's the verdict?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是你凭空变出来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, so you can just make this happen out of thin air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是担心你肚子饿了  然后万物之绿...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was just concerned about you being hungry, and the green...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  替我感谢万物之绿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, tell the green thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  这个太好吃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is, this is... It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都开始苏醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything is starting to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮萍  锯齿草  夹竹桃花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Duckweed, sawgrass, phlox flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些野葛  吵人的家伙们  天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all those kudzu, noisy bastards. Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能听到植物苏醒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can hear the plants waking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,植物比动物更加敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plants are much more sensitive than animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是它们的声音更小一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Their voices are just a little quieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们想要告诉我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they're trying to tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于"黑暗"的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About the "Darkness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上有太多超乎想象的美  艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God, there's so much unimaginable beauty out there, Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多的死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So much death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了很多  那些被腐朽侵占的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've seen things, places where the rot and decay have taken over
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁了所有生命  吞噬途经的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and destroyed all life, consuming everything in its path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么控制了你  都是在沼泽诞生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever's gotten a hold you, it was born in the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要了解这个黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to understand this darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个"腐朽"  这样我才有机会治愈你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this, this "rot", if I'm ever gonna cure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Abby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾比  艾比  等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Abby! Abby, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  等一等  等等  停下  听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Damn it! Just wait a minute. Wait. Stop. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入被腐朽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Entering this area,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌控的地区非常危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the rot has taken over, is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  但危险的植物有时候能产出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, and dangerous plants can sometimes produce
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-最有效的药物  -我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- the most effective medicine. - I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人比我更想被治愈  相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no one wants that medicine more than I do, trust me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能冒着让你丧命的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but not at the risk of losing your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是疾控中心的医生  这是我本职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a CDC doctor. This is what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警长办公室里没咖啡了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sherriff's department run out of Folgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想换个环境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just felt like a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调岗请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Transfer request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可比从吧台搬到卡座的距离远多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's more than moving from the bar to a booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖用完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're out of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  不关我事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right. None of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在警讯监控仪听到  你和几名警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, the police scanner placed you and a couple of detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚深入沼泽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}deep in the swamp last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找袭击那两名猎人的坏蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}looking for the bad boy who attacked those hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你该问艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe you should ask Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想  但我今早还没见过她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would, except I haven't seen her this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会碰巧知道她在哪吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't suppose you happen to know where she's at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用藏着掖着  莉茲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have to keep hiding it, Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾比肯定已经跟你说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure Abby already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚历克·霍兰的事  -他怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- About Alec Holland. - What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他了  莉茲  我什么都知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I've seen him, Liz. I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到他了  艾比呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've seen him? And Abby?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are they all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  上次我看到他们的时候  他们都没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't worry. Last time I saw them, they were fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但艾比在保护他  她还认为她能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But Abby's protecting him. She still thinks she can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道  让他"回来"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know, bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特  我认识你多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Matt, how long have I known you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年级就认识了  珀金老师的课上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Third grade, Mr. Perkin's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太了解你了  这幅愁眉苦脸的样子不是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Long enough to know this pensive thing isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事瞒着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾比一直在说玛雷有一股黑暗力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Abby keeps talking about this darkness in Marais,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么沼泽里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like there's this poison
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,释放出了毒物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}coming off the swamp, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得她听上去像是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you're thinking she sounds crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm thinking she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白  我跟伍德罗说了别搞这么多数字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't understand it. I told Woodrue to go easy on the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你雇用伍德罗博士  因为他是最出色的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you hired Dr. Woodrue because he's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不代表他通俗易懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doesn't mean he's easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不  亲爱的  你不必做这些的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. No, honey, you didn't have to do all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以找餐饮公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would have been happy bringing in a caterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃勒里先生这样的人习惯了吃宴席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A man like Mr. Ellery is used to catered meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他八成很少吃家常菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What he probably doesn't have much of is home cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开的药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That medication he prescribed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像让你有精神多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it really seems to be lifting your spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我感觉很放松\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's true. I feel so... relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对这个内森·埃勒里先生有什么了解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what do you know about this Mr. Nathan Ellery anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎不了解  他似乎喜欢这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very little, which seems to be the way he likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道他是秘密会议集团的高级顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just know that he's senior advisor for the Conclave Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密会议集团\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Conclave Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是间谍小说里才有的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sounds like something out of a spy novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道他们给各种各样的初创公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I know is they've given hundreds of millions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供了数亿的资金  医疗  制药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to all kinds of start-ups. Healthcare, pharmaceuticals,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器开发  航空航天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}weapons development, aerospace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让娜丁准备一壶萨泽拉克鸡尾酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I asked Nadine to whip up a pitcher of Sazerac,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合搭配开胃小菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which will pair nicely with the canapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后上杏仁鳟鱼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then, we'll move on to trout amandine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香煎法罗和芥菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}pan fried farro and mustard greens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俨然是南方美女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Playing the Southern belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是弗洛伊德送兰花来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That must be Floyd with the orchids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑德兰先生  警长找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sunderland, the Sheriff would like a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑德兰夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mrs. Sunderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯博警长  真是惊喜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheriff Cable. What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry to interrupt y'all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我找你有点事  埃弗里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I need to borrow you for a minute, Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方事务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去吧  我还有点事要忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You go on. I've got a few things to sort out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说过多少遍了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've told you a hundred times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不要不打招呼就来我家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}never to come here without calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王八蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让霍兰死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You wanted him dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你自己没胆量动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you didn't have the guts to do it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就要挟马特是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so you blackmailed Matt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我儿子拽进了一起谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You dragged my son into a fucking murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早该知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have known that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子口风不严\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}mama's boy couldn't keep his mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都知道你身体里住着毒蛇  埃弗里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I always knew that a part of you was like a goddamn snake, Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从未  从未想过它会来咬我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never, ever thought that snake was coming after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实是  一旦跟你扯上关系就会万劫不复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But the truth is, everything you touch goes to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个镇子  我  马特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this town, me, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟糕的是  整整三十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the worst part about it is for 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直对此坐视不理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just stood by and let it all happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  可我怎么不记得你之前抱怨过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, well, I don't recall you complaining
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候  我的这些勾当可给你赚了大钱呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when all my dirty business was lining your pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的  埃弗里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fuck you, Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如这样  等你不再趾高气昂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll tell you what, when you come off your high horse,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就自己过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why don't you come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯酒  然后走人吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and make yourself a drink then show yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有个会要准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got a meeting to prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备个屁  这事还没完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The hell you do. This isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历克·霍兰还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alec Holland is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No way he survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特看见他了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Matt saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他受到那种植物疾病的衍生影响而变得畸形\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He says he's been deformed by some offshoot of that plant disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但的确是霍兰  我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it's Holland all right. And I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他回到镇上说出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if he gets to town and starts talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个都会因凶杀和共谋而锒铛入狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all three of us are going down for murder and conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会处理的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这件事上你别想全身而退\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no. You will not vomit out your dirty work on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要一起处理  你和我  现在就去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna do this, you and me, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你疯了  -不  我是在保护儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You're out of your mind. - No, I'm protecting my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事没有商量的余地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this is not a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在告诉你接下来该怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is me telling you how it's gonna go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍兰  还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holland. Alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还顺利吗  -是的  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Everything okay? - Yeah, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了点事情  我要出去一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something's come up, and I gotta go out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西莉亚需要我帮忙游说某位法官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lucilia needs me to smooth things over with a certain judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的客人七点才来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our guests shouldn't be until 7:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定能及时赶回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I'll be back in plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜丁和我会准备好一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nadine and I will make sure that everything's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让他尽快回到你身边  桑德兰夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll get him back home to you as soon as I can, Mrs. Sunderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小在玛雷长大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've spent my entire childhood in Marais,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片沼泽里度过了很多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}hours in this swamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不曾见过这般郁郁葱葱的景象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I don't think I've seen it this lush before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李子结出  鲜花盛开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Plums appear, flowers bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会出现这样的奇景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How is any of this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点难以解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's, uh... It's a little hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only that it's not connected to a world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不遵循任何逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that has anything to do with logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不遵循科学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学是真实且深奥的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, science is real, it's profound,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在知道了世上还存在着其他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but now I know that there's other parts of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和科学一样深奥而自然的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that are just as profound, just as natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如万物之绿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like the green.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止于此  还有一些无形的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's more than that. There are these unseen forces
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,环绕在我们身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that play all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生死之力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forces of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最理想的状况下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the best of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生死之力互相调和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they work against each other in a, kind of, harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keeping a balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在某时某地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then, there are times and places
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更黑暗的元素  死亡与腐朽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the darker elements, the death and the rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会压倒和抑制万物之绿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It takes over, drowns out the green.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是树\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们很痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电锯  毒素以及有人一直在倒入的促进剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Chainsaws, toxins, the accelerant someone's been dumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树在愤怒地控诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's lashing out in anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要取样带回实验室  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I need to get a sample to take back to the lab. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是影响玛雷的生物异常现象的根源\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this is the source of the biological anomalies affecting Marais,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们需要弄清楚  -你没在听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- we need to understand it. - You're not listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能再往前走了  太危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not going any further. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那里可能蕴含着丰富的知识  -艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- There could be a wealth of knowledge in there... - Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许能帮助我们研制出解药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that could lead us towards a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取不到样本的话我是不会回去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not going back without a specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-桑德兰夫人  -博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Mrs. Sunderland. - Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是来告知我今晚的着装要求的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if this is about tonight's dress code,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡洛琳向我保证我会穿着合适的服装出席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Caroline assures me that I'll be in proper attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是希望能和你聊聊你的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Actually, I was hoping we could talk about your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在读你的报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been going over your report,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能在晚宴上进行的流畅的交流\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I like to keep the conversation moving at the dinner table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太理解你得出的结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was having a little trouble understanding your conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的报告不是写给外行人看的  桑德兰夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't write for a lay audience, Mrs. Sunderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的丈夫想让复杂的生物化学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If your husband wants complex biochemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更容易理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}distilled down into something more digestible,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我或许可以...  -抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- then perhaps I could, uh-- - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说得更清楚一些的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I should have been more clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我感到困惑的不是科学\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't the science that I was confused by,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你认为自己的测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was the part where you deemed your testing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得了绝对成功的那部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}an unmitigated success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从昏迷中被你唤醒的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man you revived from a coma
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被捆在轮床上  痛苦地扭动着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}left here strapped to a gurney, writhing in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副作用总是过程的一部分  桑德兰太太\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Side effects are always part of the process, Mrs. Sunderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我有一个更大的患者库可供选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perhaps if I had had a wider patient pool to select from,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们就不用谈这个了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then we wouldn't be having this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士  你不必那么戒备我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have to be defensive with me, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果时间和金钱不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If time and money weren't an issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有信心实现自己的承诺吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are you confident you could achieve what you're promising here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底为什么要谈这些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are we even having this conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃弗里在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Avery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃弗里现在不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Avery isn't here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他回来之前  你听命于我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until he returns, you'll be answering to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能还是不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有信心实现自己的承诺吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you confident you can deliver what you're promising here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No doubt in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐七点开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dinner's at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带这么多弹药来对付一个叛逃的科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some heavy duty ammo for a renegade scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次猎枪和炸药都没能弄死霍兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holland walked away from a shotgun and dynamite the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not taking any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  埃弗里  你为什么非得杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus, Avery, why did you have to go kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个王八蛋犯了个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That son of a bitch made one mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍兰知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holland knew what he was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他能老实做他的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If he just stuck to his job, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行测试  提交报告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Run his test, filed his reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他越界了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But he overstepped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他不该管的闲事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stuck his nose where it didn't belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想如果他知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, imagine if he knew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年来你倾倒废料  过度砍伐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about all the years that you were dumping and over-logging,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及炸新水道的事  想象一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and dynamiting new channels, imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我父亲的事  这片沼泽仍然亏欠我太多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The swamp still owes me a lot for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍兰差点就毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Holland was about to destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的毕生心血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything that I spent my entire life trying to achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及我一直努力为玛雷镇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all the prosperity I've been working my ass off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来的一切繁荣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to bring to this town, to Marais.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是你用于中饱私囊的繁荣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mean all the prosperity you've been putting in your back pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有给那些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And all that fucking money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾看不起你的人的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to all those people who thought you were nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  埃弗里  我以前就听过这番话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus, Avery, I've heard this speech before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得换点新说辞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've got to get new material.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的只是他没给我多少选择的余地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I'm saying is he didn't leave me much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你只是又一个受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, you're just another victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的良心让你如此不安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if your conscience is bothering you so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好让我来对付这小子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you better let me handle this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上还有配枪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've still got your service weapon.
