Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.50,0:33:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You just saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
