Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.28,0:35:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.95,0:35:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.83,0:35:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Goodnight, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.34,0:35:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住  马蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hang in there, Matty.
