Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.51,0:35:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯了个错误  马蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I made a mistake, Matty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.89,0:36:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你为什么不能告诉我  -我羞于启齿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Why couldn't you just tell me, huh? - I was ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.52,0:36:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了让埃弗里出现在你的人生中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't bear the idea of Avery being in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.68,0:36:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你把那个可怕的男人当作父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of you looking up to that horrible man as your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.69,0:36:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都是为了我  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did it all for me, huh?
