Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\b1\bord0\shad1}桑德兰公司  秘密会议集团\N玛丽亚·桑德兰  内森·埃勒里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.84,0:36:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么搞的  -我们需要进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What the hell? - We need to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.64,0:36:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  你不能来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jesus Christ, you can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.22,0:36:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽亚  马蒂失血过多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maria, Matt is bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让我们进去  -这又是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Let us in. - Who the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.06,0:36:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是弗雷德医生  我在船上给他打的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's Doctor Fred. I called him from the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.02,0:36:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  你以为我想来这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, you think I wanna be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特受了刀伤  我没法带他去医院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't exactly bring Matt to the hospital with a knife wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.27,0:36:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.78,0:36:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  带他去厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, bring him into the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.32,0:37:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.33,0:37:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了它  马蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drink it, Matty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.05,0:37:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是计划的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This was not part of the plan.
