Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.48,0:37:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.28,0:37:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伍德罗尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Woodrue did his part,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.40,0:37:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后山核桃派搞定了对方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the pecan pie sealed the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.87,0:37:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃弗里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Avery.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.37,0:37:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.72,0:38:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯  妹子  成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cheer up, buttercup. It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.19,0:38:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司是你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The company is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.94,0:38:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我无法为丈夫的死欣喜若狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Forgive me if I don't gloat over the death of my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.61,0:38:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些谎言与操纵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the lies and manipulation.
