Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.63,0:38:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有共同目标  露西莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had a common goal, Lucilia,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.38,0:38:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然目标达成了  我希望你从我的人生中消失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and now that it's done, I want you out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.60,0:38:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是自觉高我一等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You always did think you were better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走之前一定要把血迹都擦干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make sure you clean up all this blood before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.36,0:38:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上我要看到厨房一尘不染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want my kitchen spotless in the morning.
