Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.89,0:39:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想  也许我变成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been thinking, maybe there's a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样是有原因的  比如...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've become what I am, you know? Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.73,0:39:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如我身处某个更宏大的计划中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like I'm the part of some larger plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.12,0:39:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.58,0:39:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是什么样的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What kind of plan are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.33,0:39:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know, but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.25,0:39:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它比你我更加重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's bigger than you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.83,0:40:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手臂中的对抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That fight we saw in your arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.21,0:40:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我们身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.63,0:40:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遍布这片沼泽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, in this swamp.
